      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i mean like just a little bit? i dont drink a lot, just the one glass i have with dinner. i feel like i'm being too cautious. surely one glass won't actually make me stop breathing or anything? it just seems like it would make the zolpidem work way more effectively so i can finally get some rest.",
