      "content": "idk i just feel like i'm overthinking it. my friend takes stuff like this all the time and says it's fine as long as you dont go overboard. if i just take a half dose of the pill instead of a full one, would that make it safer to have my wine? i just really need to sleep and maybe a little extra relaxation would help get me there.",
